      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation activities must address the same device geometry class, fluid, and operating regime as the COU.",
      "rationale": "Validation performed on FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry under CPB-representative flow and rotational speed conditions. Blood analog fluid properties match COU. Geometry fidelity confirmed by comparison of CAD dimensions against FDA benchmark specifications."
    },
    {
